data.description: Horse property set up and ready. Endless possibilitys here, full training facility set up or horse boarding facility well built round pen,riding roping arena ,BLM close by,in a quiet location overlooking the valley this move in ready 3 bed 2 bath home includes an office that could  be a 4th bedroom, a family sized living room and 2 eating areas. Outside amenities include a 36x36 barn with stalls, tack room with 220, horse safe pens with shelters, roping arena with washed sand, and gaited pipe to irrigate the pasture.This well thought out acreage has electricity at 4 of the frost free hydrants, extra storage and plenty of parking for the RV (& a dump).
data.whatILove: Far enough out of town to enjoy peace and quiet but yet just a 5 minute drive to the grocery store.BLM right across the way to enjoy a relaxing hike or horseback ride.
